name: JARRIE's Hot Wing Hummus with Snack Factory® Pretzel Crisp® Dippers
author: JARRIE
summary: Chickpeas and spices are blended into a smooth and creamy dip that's perfect with Snack Factory® Pretzel Crisps®!
ingredients: 2 (15 ounce) cans garbanzo beans, rinsed and drained
6 tablespoons Buffalo wing sauce (such as Frank's® RedHot)
¼ cup water, or as needed for consistency
1 (7.2 ounce) package Original Snack Factory® Pretzel Crisps®
Assorted, fresh vegetable sticks cut up for dipping
directions: Combine beans, hot sauce, ranch dressing, garlic, and oil in a food processor
Pulse, adding water as necessary to improve consistency until desired consistency is reached, 8 to 10 pulses
Top with crumbled blue cheese and a drizzle of more hot sauce
Serve with Snack Factory® Pretzel Crisps® and assorted vegetables for dipping
Top with blue cheese and an optional drizzle of hot sauce
Serve with Snack Factory® Pretzel Crisps® and assorted veggie sticks like carrots and celery
